      • connectState

        void connectState(int code,
                  com.inuker.bluetooth.library.model.BleGattProfile profile,
                  boolean isOadModel)
        Connection status return
        parameters:
        code - connection status, only if the value isCode.REQUEST_SUCCESSindicates successful connection
        profile - Bluetooth properties of the device
        isOadModel - devices include two modes[Normal mode/Firmware Upgrade Mode], in most cases the normal mode, only when the device fails the firmware upgrade operation, will enter the firmware upgrade mode
